        <item>
            <title>全新 Mercedes-Benz CLA 到港，新外型设计 + 可选配杜比全景声音乐</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/mercedes-benz-cla-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mercedes-benz-cla-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/mercedes-benz-cla-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 02:57:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[车坛动向]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1196845</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平治 CLA Coupé 采用新设计前泵把、星徽图案鬼面罩和后导流器，令其运动个性更强烈，标准配置 LED High Performance 头灯和 LED 尾灯亦带来新设计。新版本增加 Hyper Blue (CLA 独有) 和 Spectral Blue 车身颜色。全新 CLA 标准配置低风阻、高光泽 18 吋五辐式 tremolite grey 轮圈，另有三种轮圈设计作选择，尺寸可达 19 吋。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002.jpg"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>高科技车厢提供新颜色和饰条配搭</h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 配备新一代 Nappa 軚环，并提供碳纤维样式、石灰木或啡色微纤维等饰条设计。 标准配置 ARTICO 人造皮革/ MICROCUT 微纤维的立体剪裁运动座椅，提供共五种车厢颜色选，择: 黑色、啡色、鼠尾草灰、钛金属灰/黑和新配搭红/黑双色。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196852" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>标准设备更齐全，可选组合更精简<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 标准设备已经包括真皮軚盘，LED 头，灯，高灯辅助系统，后泊车镜头、USB 组合、泊车组合和后视镜组合。 车身颜色、车厢颜色、饰件和轮圈等，仍可单独选择。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>最新一代 MBUX 及 Burmester 音响连杜比全景声</h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 采用了最新一代的 MBUX 「经典」提供齐全的驾驶资讯，「运动」配有抢眼的转数表，而「简约」只显示最基本资讯。 结合导航、驾驶辅助和服务模式及七种背景颜色，驾驶者可为仪表及中央屏幕作多种个人化设定。CLA Coupé 增加了 USB-C 插，头，亦提高了 USB 充电功率。 所有 USB 插头现在都会发光。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>当启用 Mercedes me app 网上服务后，新一代 MBUX 语音辅助系统在对话和学习能力上均会有所提升。例如部份指令毋须讲 &#8220;Hey Mercedes」 便能执行。 MBUX 语音辅助系统亦能解释部份车上功能。可选配的 Burmester 环回音响系统联同最新一代的 MBUX ，提供杜比全景声 (Dolby Atmos) 听觉享受，为音乐提供更多空间感、清晰度和深度。全新 CLA 加强了安全辅助系统，而且新一代泊车组合支援平衡 (S 位) 泊车，亦提供 360 度影像。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>电气化驱动系统<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新 CLA 200 中的 1.3 升四汽缸引擎 (最大马力 163 匹) 已作电气化，并与七速双离合器波箱配合。轻混能系统包括 48 伏特的电力系统，为皮带驱动的起动发电机供电。 其短暂可用的 14 匹额外马力及 150 牛顿米扭力，令起步更敏捷。 起动发电机还提高了舒适度: 除了减低引擎启动时，的震动和噪音外，它还容许关闭引擎时滑行。它还可在制动和加速过程中回收动能，为 12 伏特，电力系统和 48 伏特电池充电，在加速时提供动力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>售价<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新平治 CLA 200 现于 Mercedes-Benz Lab (新界大围车公庙路 18 号围方 2 楼 201 号舖) 公开展示，售价由 $438,800 起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
